Your choice of measure defines your entire visualization and determines the scope of your exploration. To change measures, click the "Count of Rows" default and select "Sum" or other options. Add a second measure to see 2 visualizations side by side.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition.

To open the Measures selection menu, click "Count of Rows" and select a new measure. Click "Unique" to count unique occurrences of a measure or dimension.
